name: Tezzard Bico Doce
description:
Very little is known about this creature, the only reports are that it has a shape that resembles a lizard and that it has the power to transform into other folklore creatures, disturbing and confusing those who enter the forest looking for the true creatures. <Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>


[This card is a special edition in tribute to the Tezzarzz project, by omgidrawedit.]
